metadata.name: 𝑀𝒜𝐿𝒜 𝐻𝑜𝓉 𝒞𝒽𝒾𝓁𝒾 𝒪𝒾𝓁 - 𝒮𝒾𝓏𝓏𝓁𝒾𝓃𝑔 & 𝒯𝒾𝓃𝑔𝓁𝒾𝓃𝑔 𝒟𝑒𝓁𝒾𝑔𝒽𝓉!!!
metadata.description:
🔥 🌶 🙀 - Hello fellow connoisseurs of Chinese Cuisine - & that MALA SENSATION!!! 🙀 🌶 🔥

Today I am sharing an old video I made of my experiment making 𝙈𝙖𝙡𝙖 𝙃𝙤𝙩 𝘾𝙝𝙞𝙡𝙞 𝙊𝙞𝙡! It's a 𝘔𝘢𝘭𝘢 Project!

The cool thing about hot chili oil is that it makes your mouth tingle and numb - and this video will make your mind tingle and numb! Fun!!! 🔥 🌶 (110% Satisfaction Guaranteed! 👌🏻 )
